8.10.20  2:25 pm   thoughts on ohio

      scientists estimate that the average person lives in ohio

8.10.20  2:25 pm   Hey I really love your videos/songs. I love you too. Are you working on something big right now?

      if you consider 'making videos and songs for the rest of my life' big

8.10.20  2:17 pm   My apologies for the needless specificity, but in regards to your hard left turn into not learning 3d animation anymore for the time being did this occur because you feel you have learned the necessary things to propel significant developments in the video making department that you've been pursuing?

     NOT EVEN CLOSE but in reality i'm sure i probably have

      Or did you get distracted making and picking songs and there is much more to be done in the 3d animation department?

     no i didn't get distracted with song-picking, what happened was i had 3 panic attacks in a row about the production train being paused for so long. that's the signal to go ahead. this is standard procedure, i've known this

8.10.20  2:15 pm   Thoughts on the colour pink?

      it's just right

8.10.20  2:07 pm   why is the first day of school so long

      because it's so memorable. because it contains so many new things for you

      no

      coaxing someone into a live interview scenario and then asking a whole bunch of questions that start with "does it bother you that...."

      i would say so

8.10.20  1:48 pm   What is your biggest inspiration when making music?

      the whole world

      Tuesday, August 11, 2020 3:37:29 PM

      while not being true that sounds surprisingly accurate

8.10.20  1:41 pm   DO YOU EDIT YOURSELF?

      that's preposterous. who do you think i am

      making songs and videos for the rest of my life

      because some of the questions are the same

      what the heck is a weekend

8.10.20  12:51 pm   why hasn't anybody asked any questions for two days? that's sad :(

      you may have fallen victim to a bit of 'false information'. i've received thousands of questions over the past 2 days. in fact, at least 3 other questions were asked within less than 60 seconds before you asked yours

8.10.20  12:49 pm   Your music/videos make me feel good about staying in this world and I am so grateful they exist. Have you ever struggled with mental health/wanting to leave this world?

     the thing that usually happens is i want to go even further IN to the world, and i struggle with fear that i might not be able to

     If so, what helps? 

     making up a folk tale about it

8.10.20  12:25 pm   Where does your channels aesthetic come from?

      the gutter

8.10.20  11:58 am   What are your plans on uploading videos?

     the plan is to make the videos first, then unpload them

     (Sorry if I seem rude)

8.10.20  11:53 am   do you music?

      oh that would explain a lot

8.10.20  11:51 am   how do you do stuff

      impossible. it can't be done

8.10.20  11:47 am   When are you going to make a new song?

      immediately very soon, but that's only part of the picture. the rest of the picture is i'm gonna make more songs after that, and also videos

8.10.20  11:44 am   what's your opinion on giraffe?

      they are not only tall, but also very wide

8.10.20  11:17 am   when you compose songs, do you go off a basic structure or completely freelance it? hope you're having a good day!

      sometimes i trick myself into thinking i'm going to use a structure but then i don't. but still, often, if i'm totally freestyling it, it very often falls into structure, even if it's not the one i would have expected

      sort of

     songwriting

     to have lots of songs, to make into recordings and videos, for your listening/viewing enjoyment
